# Data Dictionary — bentley2023_disruption

## Data source
SciSciNet — Citation network 1945-2010
Access: public; Provenance: SciSciNet local

## Key variables
- Unit of analysis: paper
- Time window: 1945-2010
- Sample N: 469855
- Filter rules: require CD score, require citations

## Indicator definitions
- Formula: mCD5(t) = Σ(cit_i * CD5_i) / Σ(cit_i)
- Parameters: citation weighting
- Computation steps: compute CD5, weight by citations, groupby year
